§7§oUse the arcane prison key

§fThe broken remains of Asgard carry some traces of a strong magic, which does appear to be the same force I felt while being constrained by the guardians.
He who dominated this magic, the warden of Asgard, the last wolf, the last of the Aesir, the Sympan spirit, answered my call.
The oath is broken, the enemy has won, but at least these poor souls are now free.
And who knows, maybe they may come to my aid at some point in the future...
